Class ScanTask

java.lang.Object
  visual.test.ScanTask
Direct Known Subclasses:
RecursiveScan
public abstract class ScanTask
extends java.lang.Object

The Scan Tasks each use different algorithms to accomplish the same goal: iterating through every file on a HDD/partition/folder, beginning with a supplied "root" folder
